Genital plate consisting of 13 setae in male (preadult) and 17–21 in female (
Figs. 15 & 16
). Male ventral organ absent. Anal valves with numerous acuminate setae; each lateral valve with a0 and 2 a 1 setae; upper valve with a0, b 0, 2 b 1, 2 b 2 , c 0, 2 c 1 and 2 c 2 (after
Yoshii 1996
